caption.title: Duration of viral transmission per island as a function of Log(10) cumulative number of cases including first two months of dengue case occurrence and serotype.
caption.p: Shown are the best fit lines from the GLM loglinear regression and the adjusted probabilities (partial residuals) from the multivariate analysis. Serotype colour codes are: DENV-1 red; DENV-2 green; DENV-3 blue; DENV-4 cyan; DENV1+3 pink.
